                        <note rend="inline" type="source">721.23/1567: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Minister in Switzerland</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Wilson</hi></persName>), <hi rend="italic">at
                                Geneva</hi></head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-04-12T18:00:00-05:00">April 12, 1933—6
                                p.m.</date></dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>94. Your telegram No. 167, April 7, 9 p.m. was repeated to Bogotá. The
                            following reply from Mr. Caffery is repeated to you for your
                            information:</p>
                        <p>(Here follows Telegram No. 44, April 11, 2 p.m. from Bogotá.)</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi></signed></closer>
